    ('a268eeba-fe8d-5372-8dcc-76de87baa789', 'call', 'demo:doc:act:59', 'Call — Coppell Distribution Center RTU replacement, phase one (2026-02-10): Inbound from Russ Vandermeer, procurement at Coppell Distribution Center: RFP for a full RTU replacement program, 28 units on the main building.', '2026-02-10T13:45:00-05:00'),
    ('a268eeba-fe8d-5372-8dcc-76de87baa789', 'upload', 'demo:doc:act:60', 'Meeting — Coppell Distribution Center RTU replacement, phase one (2026-02-24): Depot walkthrough with Russ and Ines Calloway (ops): the units are 15-year-old builder-grade, three already on portable backup. They want a phased replacement over two quarters.', '2026-02-24T12:05:00-05:00'),
    ('a268eeba-fe8d-5372-8dcc-76de87baa789', 'email', 'demo:doc:act:61', 'Email — Coppell Distribution Center RTU replacement, phase one (2026-03-03): Sent the phased replacement proposal: $96,000 for phase one (10 units), crane and controls included.', '2026-03-03T12:00:00-05:00'),
    ('a268eeba-fe8d-5372-8dcc-76de87baa789', 'upload', 'demo:doc:act:62', 'Note — Coppell Distribution Center RTU replacement, phase one (2026-03-15): Competitive heat: Apex Air Systems is bidding aggressively; Russ shares numbers freely to push price.', '2026-03-15T12:50:00-05:00'),
    ('a268eeba-fe8d-5372-8dcc-76de87baa789', 'call', 'demo:doc:act:63', 'Call — Coppell Distribution Center RTU replacement, phase one (2026-03-23): Russ: Apex came in ''well under'' our number. He asked for our best and final.', '2026-03-23T16:45:00-05:00'),
    ('a268eeba-fe8d-5372-8dcc-76de87baa789', 'email', 'demo:doc:act:64', 'Email — Coppell Distribution Center RTU replacement, phase one (2026-04-06): Best-and-final sent: held scope, trimmed 4% with a value-engineering swap on the curbs. Held the line beyond that — below our floor the project loses money.', '2026-04-06T13:10:00-05:00'),
    ('a268eeba-fe8d-5372-8dcc-76de87baa789', 'upload', 'demo:doc:act:65', 'Meeting — Coppell Distribution Center RTU replacement, phase one (2026-04-15): Final pitch to Ines on lifecycle cost: our units carry a 10-year compressor warranty vs Apex''s 5. She was sympathetic; procurement owns the call.', '2026-04-15T11:00:00-05:00'),
    ('a268eeba-fe8d-5372-8dcc-76de87baa789', 'call', 'demo:doc:act:66', 'Call — Coppell Distribution Center RTU replacement, phase one (2026-04-21): Russ confirmed they are signing with Apex Air Systems at roughly 18% under our final number.', '2026-04-21T14:45:00-05:00'),
    ('a268eeba-fe8d-5372-8dcc-76de87baa789', 'upload', 'demo:doc:act:67', 'Note — Coppell Distribution Center RTU replacement, phase one (2026-05-02): Marked closed_lost on price. Post-mortem filed: we will not chase Apex below floor; flagged Coppell for a service-rescue campaign next winter.', '2026-05-02T16:10:00-05:00'),
